      'Built the <strong>Projects featureset</strong> end-to-end: designed the UX and implemented an interactive CSV upload pipeline with real-time validation, normalisation, and error recovery using TanStack React Table, React Query, Redux, Rx.js, TypeScript, and io-ts.',
      'Co-built <strong>Sayari Map</strong> from concept to MVP in under six months as one of three engineers, opening an entirely new customer segment in geospatial risk and supply chain screening.',
